-- First, let's see what we're working with
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_islands FROM places WHERE type = 'island';

-- Get a sample of islands and their corresponding atoll names from island_guides
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.slug, ig.atoll 
FROM places p 
LEFT JOIN island_guides ig ON p.id = ig.placeId 
WHERE p.type = 'island' 
LIMIT 5;

-- Get atoll mapping
SELECT a.id, a.name FROM atolls a LIMIT 5;
